    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1668516836590-x200.jpg",
