          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1668516836590-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is browned, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>coconut stock</strong> and cook, covered, for 10 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1668516840537-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
