            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>curried chicken breast enchilada filling</strong> (reserving some of the curry sauce for later) between your <strong>seeded tortillas</strong></p><p>Roll up the <strong>tortillas</strong> tightly – these are your <strong>enchiladas</strong></p><p>Place the <strong>enchiladas</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, with the seam side down</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1668516851268-x200.jpg",
